Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.35,0:00:24.30,Default,op,0,0,0,,Under the skies that are still unknown to me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.30,0:00:28.40,Default,op,0,0,0,,I know, you're doing just the same -
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.40,0:00:29.98,Default,op,0,0,0,,Dreaming
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.98,0:00:35.24,Default,op,0,0,0,,Just a small glow\NFrom those great days
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.24,0:00:38.12,Default,op,0,0,0,,Is what dragging you along
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.12,0:00:41.87,Default,op,0,0,0,,Giving you faith and some comfort
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.87,0:00:45.79,Default,op,0,0,0,,Under the sun that scorches badly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.00,0:00:52.17,Default,op,0,0,0,,I only want to see your guise
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.17,0:00:53.91,Default,op,0,0,0,,But instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.91,0:00:59.18,Default,op,0,0,0,,I only watch \NWith tears on my face
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.18,0:01:04.77,Default,op,0,0,0,,As you slowly disappear in this noon haze
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.77,0:01:07.76,Default,op,0,0,0,,We're alone \NWe're alone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.76,0:01:11.31,Default,op,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,1000)}Walking this world on our own
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.36,0:01:16.53,Default,op,0,0,0,,{\fade(1000,0)}Looking for each other since long ago
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.53,0:01:22.49,Default,op,0,0,0,,In the end, in the end, \NAfter the day we finally meet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.49,0:01:27.00,Default,op,0,0,0,,{\b1\bord1\blur1\t(2100,2200,\shad3\blur3\c&HABADD8&)}We won't ever have to say "Goodbye"
Comment: 0,0:01:33.06,0:01:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{OP END}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.03,0:02:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,7 to 5, 2 to 6, 0 to 6. 2 sets to 1.\NMatch won by Sekiguchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.87,0:02:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You can still participate in the second round.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.42,0:02:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,In 6 days you will be admitted to a repechage match.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.09,0:02:32.10,Default,ep titile,0,0,0,,{\bord4\blur15\3c&HCEAC95&\t(0,1000,\bord0\blur0)\c&HFBFAF9&\fnGabriola\fs48\frz359.6\fscx169\fscy143\pos(358,342)}Episode 5 \N\N\N\NThere's no turning back now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.20,0:02:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.69,0:02:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You are afraid not a single worthy fight will take place?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.16,0:02:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Makes sense. \NAfter a wrist injury, Midorikawa left for an unknown location.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.79,0:02:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka was destroyed in the first round by an outsider. \NThe sacred rivalry between you two seems to be fading.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:03:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,However, Hiromi still has the repechage match.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.47,0:03:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.61,0:03:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She will definitely surmount it once again. \NHiromi always does.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.07,0:03:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi, a phone call for you! It's Maki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.14,0:03:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, hello, Hiromi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.63,0:03:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, you're free the night after tomorrow? \NLet's go out together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.14,0:03:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch the fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.16,0:03:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! There will be a plaza on the third pier. \NIt's certain to have a splendid view!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.52,0:03:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The real summer is already over. \NLet's bring it to a conclusion with a lively party. Party!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to cheer you up, \Ncooping up in a room is no good for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.26,0:03:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter with you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.73,0:04:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Oka! What's with that attitude of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.95,0:04:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,To the baseline at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You are on a court. \NWhat else are you thinking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.94,0:04:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who don't want to work should go the hell home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.43,0:04:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo, I knew it all along.\NTodo, you've lost your match.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.78,0:04:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Standing all alone on a rainy court, \Nshedding big bitter tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.37,0:04:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're far away...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.09,0:04:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you now, Todo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.39,0:05:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do a single thing for you now.\NIt's so frustrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.22,0:05:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I could see your smile in front of me again, \Nhear your voice again...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,My soul would be by such a great extent relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Presently, I lose track easily \Nof wherever I'm going and whatever I'm doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.52,0:05:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, Coach Katsura scolded me especially hard. \NHe sent me home. But where is the place I can call home?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.52,0:05:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,1000)}I don't have a place such as home.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.03,0:05:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(1000,0)}I want to see you... I want to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.01,0:05:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.86,0:05:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,While exhorting me{ for battle} with every his word, \NTodo was shipwrecked himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.33,0:05:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,While I'm still so useless to{/ unable to help} him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.88,0:05:50.88,Default,,0,0,10,,{\an8\b0\fnVerdana}Japanese Tourist Agency \NTours in the USA
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.39,0:05:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo, I want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.89,0:06:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.03,0:06:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet, I was here for like 15 minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.14,0:06:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's quickly get some cotton candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So, feeling better now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.81,0:06:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,More or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Something just went wrong in that last match, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.57,0:06:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure to definitely win in the repechage match, Hiromi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.81,0:06:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi, is your cotton candy unflavored?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.94,0:06:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Maki...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.89,0:06:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.47,0:06:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I made up my mind, Maki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.24,0:06:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it? I didn't hear a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I made up...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,My mind! I'm going to America!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:06:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.48,0:07:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to New York.\NI'm going to see Todo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.98,0:07:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what you have decided...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.94,0:07:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.18,0:07:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't see that coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.82,0:07:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You are such a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.99,0:07:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand you, Hiromi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.80,0:07:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Refusing the repechage match?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.77,0:07:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Please suspend my practices for some time as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:07:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.25,0:07:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka, I understand your humiliation \Nafter losing in the first round.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.01,0:08:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But do you hope to wash the shame away this way? \NWash away your bond with Ochou?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.68,0:08:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to. But nothing else is helping. \NI can't concentrate at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.68,0:08:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how hard I try to...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.78,0:08:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is the reason? The reason!?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.19,0:08:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me then. Which thing do you consider \Nthe most precious in your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.01,0:08:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me, Oka!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's tennis. Ever since I was 16, \NI decided to make it the meaning of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.93,0:08:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Not when I was 11 nor 18.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the time came now\Nfor me to be completely confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.46,0:08:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,In such moments, \Ndo you wonder what Munakata would have said?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.97,0:08:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Luckily for you I'm not Munakata!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.96,0:08:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,For that very reason, \NI won't waste my time on someone who is not devoted!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.15,0:08:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You need a passport now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Going to America is not such a big deal today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.21,0:08:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, gotta pick a plane first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.23,0:08:57.43,Default,sign,0,0,10,,{\an8\b0\fnVerdana}International Travel Agency
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.42,0:09:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If they offer you different cost options, \Njust pick the cheapest one safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.41,0:09:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, it's the money issue \Nthat is most worrisome for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.89,0:09:06.91,Default,sign,0,0,10,,{\an8\b0\fnVerdana}ATM \NCash withdrawal
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:13.92,Default,sign,0,0,10,,{\an8\b0\fnVerdana\fade(2000,0)}Payment details of the ¥61,000 bill
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though it's minimal fare, \Nwill it be enough for 3 nights?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.98,0:09:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Maki...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.59,0:09:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We always help each other when in trouble, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.07,0:09:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the kind of occasion \NI worked part-time for.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.85,0:09:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But you'll be broke then... {/ But I can't take it off you...}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.36,0:09:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop saying such nonsense! \NYou really need to get there, don't you? To New York?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.61,0:09:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well! I'll have to go with you then! \NIs that what you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't hesitate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.33,0:09:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Maki, thank you.\NReally, thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.02,0:09:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure you are steady in your feet? \NYou will have to face serious matters soon! Cheer up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.02,0:10:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back. \NBy the way, Ms. Ryuzaki called you by phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.94,0:10:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Madame Butterfly?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.10,0:10:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for calling you out at such an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.16,0:10:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No... Nevermind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.54,0:10:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you tell me a thing about Oka?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I know nothing at all!\NNot a single thing, I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.54,0:10:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Aikawa, please bear in mind \NI've been constantly looking at Oka ever since Nishi High.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.05,0:10:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Both like her mentor and like her rival. \NBut most of all - like a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.97,0:10:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.19,0:10:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard it from my father.\NOka relinquished her right for a repechage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.95,0:10:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How come Oka gave up on that match?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Ms. Aikawa. What made her step back? \NBe so kind to let me know it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.67,0:10:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I know... nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.64,0:11:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's about Todo after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.02,0:11:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.15,0:11:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is the time of paramount importance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.63,0:11:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Both for you and Todo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.52,0:11:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi, this is the thing I dreaded the most. \NAs a player, I wanted you to avoid this path more than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.83,0:11:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The path you started treading on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.70,0:11:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.66,0:11:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Madame Butterfly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.35,0:12:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a rare sight. \NGoing for a recreation?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.63,0:12:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,At this time, it's common to see you on a special court of Park Hill. \NTurns out you're a human as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm just meeting someone. Oka that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.37,0:12:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That is Oka?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.37,0:12:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, would you mind if I come along?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.83,0:12:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Be my guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Such matters are not to be discussed by phone. Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.32,0:12:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard it from Ms. Aikawa. Everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.03,0:12:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, one coffee. "America."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Your flight departures at 6 PM tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.17,0:12:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.36,0:13:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You relinquished the repechage match. Gave up a chance. \NAfter making it this far, you should not just turn away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.89,0:13:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.92,0:13:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi, I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.16,0:13:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.38,0:13:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just no use for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.66,0:13:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you alright? Feeling dizzy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.26,0:13:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.22,0:13:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.32,0:13:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.29,0:13:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Does Coach Katsura know? \NAbout your New York trip and everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.13,0:13:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I have not told him anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.88,0:14:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I wonder if learning the truth \Nwill make him rather sad or happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.38,0:14:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably better if you make him know yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.47,0:14:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,For everyone of us, treasuring just a single person \Nwould never do good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.06,0:14:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a little jealous...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.07,0:14:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were you, I'd be relentlessly tentative, \Nchanging my mind back and forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.13,0:14:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I will always be happy to see you back. \NOn the court.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.59,0:14:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Hiromi. \NI didn't say a word to Madame Butterfly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.67,0:14:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.81,0:14:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, if your tomorrow's plane is at 6 PM, \Nshould I come to see you off around 3?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No need. I want to go on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.68,0:14:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, I think I'd better go there alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.03,0:14:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.26,0:15:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a big deal, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.02,0:15:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,New York, here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.33,0:15:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Promise me then \Nto come back with a shining smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.20,0:15:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.80,0:15:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,When your family noticed, what did you say? \NYou certainly didn't tell the whole truth, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.26,0:15:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,My parents would have gotten ireful, \Ndemanding to follow me along{ in this case}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.93,0:15:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You can say you went on a trip with me, \Nto the Kamikochi Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.38,0:15:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I already said it would be Karuizawa. Play along.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.15,0:15:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi, can I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.78,0:15:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.48,0:15:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, this is a clarificant{/ gastrin?}. \NA treatment for distention.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.04,0:15:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't drink raw water, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.82,0:16:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,When moving to a new place, \Nyou need to get used to the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.92,0:16:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.06,0:16:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't sleep exposed to a draught.\NAnd get along with Maki, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.05,0:16:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.18,0:16:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.01,0:16:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.89,0:16:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka! Get in. I'll give you a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.45,0:16:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.28,0:16:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. \NI'll get you to the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.33,0:16:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But... Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi, have you already left?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.21,0:17:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you are already gone after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.47,0:17:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, my!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.48,0:17:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Maki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.03,0:17:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother... Aryagh! \NI mean... It's you, mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.42,0:17:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you in Karuizawa with Hiromi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.98,0:18:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll leave you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.15,0:18:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I have always been eager to behold you play.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.05,0:18:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And I truly hope to behold it afterwards too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.76,0:18:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.02,0:18:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, flight 118.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.73,0:18:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A dream... This is all like a one big dream I'm having.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.21,0:18:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I may have let down some people, \Nbut this is just a dream, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.70,0:18:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.04,0:18:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo, I so much want to see you before I wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.79,0:18:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Flight to New York, departing at 18:00, \Nis now ready to accept its passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.80,0:19:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The seventh gate is waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.14,0:19:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.94,0:19:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.66,0:19:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.68,0:19:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.37,0:19:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.68,0:19:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Coach Katsura...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.68,0:19:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me where you are now! Oka!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.05,0:19:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Coach...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.65,0:19:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.13,0:19:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,At Narita Airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.40,0:19:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.95,0:19:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have enough cash?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.69,0:19:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have enough cash \Nto settle in New York without having to sleep on the streets?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.82,0:19:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.84,0:19:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, make the best of this trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.03,0:20:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,YOU BIG DUMMY!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.10,0:20:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,New York you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.64,0:21:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how it is... \NHer sudden departure looked strange all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.11,0:21:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Father, Mother, I betrayed your trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka is... No, your daughter is \Nnot a simple-minded lady at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.16,0:21:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And Todo as well\Nis not a simple-minded young man at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.77,0:21:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no turning back now.
Comment: 0,0:22:10.29,0:22:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{ED START}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.87,0:22:21.62,Default,ed,0,0,0,,There is one song I cannot ever forget
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.62,0:22:27.25,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Still, there's a face I'm willing to forget
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.25,0:22:30.21,Default,ed,0,0,0,,With her feelings mixed up,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.21,0:22:33.09,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Alice got completely lost
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.09,0:22:38.28,Default,ed,0,0,0,,The midst of summer \NBrought her into one tricky love maze
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.60,0:22:45.19,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I want you to hug tightly\NAnd never let go of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.19,0:22:50.57,Default,ed,0,0,0,,One scared and timid tiny girl
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.57,0:22:57.45,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I quite remember our very first kiss \NAnd the beginning of all of this
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.03,0:23:03.87,Default,ed,0,0,0,,While birds were singing for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.94,0:23:13.06,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I'll take a car and take a lonely trip
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.06,0:23:18.26,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I know it'll bring me \NTo the seashore
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.26,0:23:21.31,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Where only the the sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.31,0:23:24.35,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Dazzlingly bright,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.35,0:23:29.88,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Could witness my long-awaited happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.32,0:23:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Aikawa Maki here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.84,0:23:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi has finally arrived in New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.75,0:23:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But apparently, Todo left his apartment. \NHiromi is so unlucky...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.57,0:23:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,However, a lucky encounter follows.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.92,0:23:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She suddenly runs into Midorikawa Ranko.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.76,0:23:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now everything is fine, Hiromi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.43,0:23:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're with Midorikawa now, \Nso you two will definitely find Todo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.80,0:24:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming soon: \N"New York, the city where Todo is."
